{"id":"b998feb3-9f50-4434-930a-e7cbc9b7e442","type":"SprintAdded","timestamp":1776848975735,"actor":"manager","projectId":"proj_1776847192658_clz2mby18","data":{"id":"sprint_1776848975734_pof4ndyfo","name":"Sprint 4: Convert CLI to Web App","description":"Replace the CLI entrypoint with an Express web server serving a chat-style browser UI on port 5002. Users interact with the orchestrator through a web page instead of the terminal. Keep all existing agent logic (orchestrator, weather agent, research agent) intact — only change the I/O layer from CLI to HTTP/HTML.","priority":"high","status":"pending"},"prevHash":"ae3a21ce4389eb5e9334f361bf59783a370215935b82e1f2767ac2bef1afcde4"}
{"id":"8d70e996-bce6-4c40-9e19-bbeeb4432155","type":"TasksGenerated","timestamp":1776848975739,"actor":"manager","projectId":"proj_1776847192658_clz2mby18","data":{"sprintId":"sprint_1776848975734_pof4ndyfo","tasks":[{"id":"task_1776848975739_0_tebzg","title":"Add Express server with API endpoint","description":"Install express and @types/express. Create src/server.ts as the new entrypoint: an Express app on port 5002 with a POST /api/chat endpoint that accepts {prompt: string}, calls runOrchestrator(prompt), and returns {response: string} as JSON. Add a GET / route that serves the static HTML frontend. Update package.json scripts so 'dev' and 'start' launch the server instead of the CLI.","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"id":"task_1776848975739_1_lcvhv","title":"Create browser chat UI","description":"Create a public/index.html with a simple but clean chat interface: a message display area, a text input, and a send button. Use inline CSS for a modern dark-themed chat layout. JavaScript fetches POST /api/chat with the user's prompt and displays the response. Show a loading indicator while waiting for the agent response. No framework needed — vanilla HTML/CSS/JS.","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"id":"task_1776848975739_2_61jlv","title":"Add sample prompt buttons to the UI","description":"Add clickable sample prompt buttons above the input (e.g. 'Weather in SF', 'Explain managed agents', 'Weather in Paris') so users can quickly test both routing paths without typing. Clicking a button populates and submits the prompt automatically.","status":"pending","priority":"medium"},{"id":"task_1776848975739_3_18v9i","title":"Add agent routing indicator to responses","description":"Modify the /api/chat response to include which agent handled the request (weather-agent or research-agent) alongside the response text. Display this routing info as a subtle label above each response in the chat UI so users can see the orchestrator's classification in action.","status":"pending","priority":"medium"}]},"prevHash":"e8e23014df8c017c16feffa79cae226357e4abeab3e3279cb66a7b0373d78b73"}
{"id":"4b47def6-0eaf-4033-9ba6-d18f750d3fd5","type":"SprintExecutionStarted","timestamp":1776848977278,"actor":"system","projectId":"proj_1776847192658_clz2mby18","data":{"sprintId":"sprint_1776848975734_pof4ndyfo","sprintName":"Sprint 4: Convert CLI to Web App","taskCount":4,"isReExecution":false},"prevHash":"6fc37244ab681293668fe505a68766f540b7a3d8c318e2a460bc17ffb2c4fb27"}
{"id":"cf24e5a3-5992-43d4-99fc-6dc02b2955ab","type":"SprintAdded","timestamp":1776848977353,"actor":"manager","projectId":"proj_1776847192658_clz2mby18","data":{"id":"sprint_1776848977352_jcdscsrps","name":"Sprint 4: Web App UI","description":"Convert the CLI POC into a proper web app. Add an Express server that exposes the orchestrator as a REST API, and build a React + MUI chat interface on the frontend so users can type prompts and see agent responses in the browser at port 5002.","priority":"high","status":"pending"},"prevHash":"df61dbcd50e10a3a87ef1cf178d3d3795f9e2c87e2e8522c3ce9d7b7f82692ae"}
{"id":"c223800a-7a15-4a13-aab1-04b2d277c73f","type":"TasksGenerated","timestamp":1776848977372,"actor":"manager","projectId":"proj_1776847192658_clz2mby18","data":{"sprintId":"sprint_1776848977352_jcdscsrps","tasks":[{"id":"task_1776848977370_0_qags8","title":"Add Express API server with /api/chat endpoint","description":"Install express and cors. Create src/server.ts that imports runOrchestrator and exposes POST /api/chat accepting { prompt: string } and returning { response: string }. The server should listen on port 5002. Add a 'server' script to package.json that runs this with ts-node.","status":"pending","priority":"critical"},{"id":"task_1776848977371_1_vmq3g","title":"Create React + MUI frontend","description":"Create a client/ directory with a React app (Vite + React + TypeScript). Install @mui/material, @emotion/react, @emotion/styled. Build a single-page chat UI: a text input at the bottom, a scrollable message history above it, and a Send button. Use MUI components (Box, TextField, Button, Paper, Typography). Color scheme: ocean (primary blue tones). Font: Inter. On submit, POST to /api/chat and display the agent's response in the message list. Show a loading state while waiting.","status":"pending","priority":"critical"},{"id":"task_1776848977371_2_7jqka","title":"Configure Vite proxy and update dev scripts","description":"In client/vite.config.ts, add a proxy so /api requests from the frontend dev server forward to http://localhost:5002. Update package.json root scripts: 'dev' should start both the Express server (port 5002) and the Vite dev server (port 5173) concurrently using the concurrently package. Update 'build' to also build the client. Add a 'start' script that serves the built client as static files from Express.","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"id":"task_1776848977371_3_8qgof","title":"Display agent routing trace in the UI","description":"The orchestrator logs routing decisions (weather-agent vs research-agent) to the server console. Modify the /api/chat endpoint to capture which agent was used (weather or research) and include it in the API response as { response: string, agentType: 'weather' | 'research' | 'other' }. In the frontend, show a small chip/badge on each agent message indicating which sub-agent handled the request (e.g. 'weather-agent' or 'research-agent').","status":"pending","priority":"medium"}]},"prevHash":"7a0bf7c0afcc516ee8f79547f36ff6a3762d4138c33264ff902c783e9fd83648"}
